properties.areaDesc: Norwood MI to 5NM West of Mackinac Bridge including Little Traverse Bay; Grand Traverse Bay south of a line Grand Traverse Light to Norwood MI
properties.headline: Gale Warning issued January 10 at 3:08PM EST until January 12 at 4:00AM EST by NWS Gaylord MI
properties.description:
* WHAT...Highest gusts up to 40 kt and highest waves around 8
feet expected.

* WHERE...Grand Traverse Bay south of a line Grand Traverse
Light to Norwood MI and Norwood MI to 5NM West of Mackinac
Bridge including Little Traverse Bay.

* WHEN...From 4 PM Saturday to 4 AM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Strong winds will cause hazardous highest waves
which could capsize or damage vessels and reduce visibility.
properties.instruction:
Mariners should alter plans to avoid these hazardous conditions.
Remain in port, seek safe harbor, alter course, and/or secure the
vessel for severe conditions.

NWSheadline: GALE WARNING IN EFFECT FROM 4 PM SATURDAY TO 4 AM EST SUNDAY
